               <p>I searched this man's lodgings, and found the things that are in this handkerchief.</p>
               <p>(Produced and deposed to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I leave my defence to my counsel.</p>
               <p>The prisoner's counsel called two witnesses who gave him a good character.</p>
